snippet.title: Shadowgrounds Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy now at https://www.humblebundle.com/store

Shadowgrounds is an epic sci-fi game that blends addictive oldshool gameplay and modern technology into one big, nasty alien-slaughtering carnage fest. The adrenaline-pumping, top-down gameplay gives you a better view of the battlefield and allows you to use your gear to its full potential.
